version_description: This one is just going off of one of the many live versions of out there. Most of the ones I've heard are played in D. The D-Dmaj7-D6-D progression may or may not go throughout the song.
This is just the version my brother taught me. For the strumming, just play what feels right.
Chords are somewhat different than in the other versions.
Added in the D-Dmaj7-D6-Dmaj7 pattern a few more times.
